title: TeleAtlas Maps 2013-2014 Scandinavia for Blaupunkt TravelPilot D
description:
TeleAtlas Sat Nav Scandinavia 2013-2014 for Blaupunkt TravelPilot DX


Denmark, Sweden, Norway and Finland


 Including major roads of Europe

 

This last edition of the DX portfolio contains for the loyally DX customers
a free of charge MERIAN SCOUT travel guide!


Product Highlights
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ ~100% detailed street network for Denmark, Sweden, Norway and Finland.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ The border region of Germany including Schleswig-Holstein, Hamburg and the Northern part of Mecklenburg-Vorpommern is also covered with detailed street network.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Door-to-door route guidance in Denmark, Finland, Norway, Sweden and the border region of Germany.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Feeling hungry, need to find a parking spot or want to top up on fuel? Count on many Points of Interest (POI) such as restaurants and car parks.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Updated official TMC code lists for Sweden and Germany. Dynamic route guidance on highways in Denmark also possible.*
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Updates include lots of new information such as new streets, new residential areas, new traffic situations and much, much more.
* Availability depends on the navigation system.
